data.description: Bright & spacious second floor unit! Vaulted ceilings & skylights. Wood laminate floors throughout. 6 panel white doors throughout. Huge walk-in closet off the foyer. Living room/ dining combo with sliding glass door out to the balcony. Eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting, & another entrance to the balcony. Huge primary suite with two closets & large private bathroom featuring double bowl sinks, separate tub, & walk-in shower. 1 car garage. Park, playground, 390 highway, and Metra station only a few blocks away. Close to shopping & the Boomers stadium.
